a_machita23" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chima Machida</a>将于12月13日星期三发行她的第一张迷你专辑“ The Pages”。</p><p>为了纪念专辑的发行，Chima Machida将被任命为HMV＆Books Shibuya商店的经理一天，并将在12月13日星期三举行两次照片会议，包括交出活动限时的名片。</p><p>在每家HMV商店购买2500日元（包括税）的人还将在同一时间举行一项活动，将在先到先得的基础上以先到先得的方式获得“ Machida Chima X HMV Fair Limited Chare”。<a href="https://www.hmv.co.jp/news/article/231108125/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>以获取公正的详细信息。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000743.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AnyColor Co.，Ltd。新闻发布</a></p><h2>现在出售4个“ Vee”才能的欢迎商品</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-jpg.webp 650w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/11/4a20f3845010a93dd55785120d0b084c-kix.ar2pt4nugt2v-150x150.webp 150w" width="650" height="650" /></a></p><p> Sony Music Entertainment Inc.的虚拟人才开发和管理项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/_vee_official_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vee</a> ”已开始为其虚拟才能<a href="https://twitter.com/ukiuki_unico" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yuniko Uki</a> ， <a href="https://twitter.com/HasumiSahiro" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sahiro Hasumi</a> ， <a href="https://twitter.com/hisumi_rihito" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hibumi</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/MememoriAn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Morian Meme</a>出售欢迎商品。</p><p> “欢迎锡徽”，“欢迎丙烯酸摊位”和“欢迎迷你横幅”。</p><p><a href="https://shop.vee-official.jp/s/ve01/?ima=5455" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>以获取销售地点。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000079.0000